_sText:
Final release of gg_watchtower.

Changes include:
Brush alignments fixed.
Tower ladder replaced with model and extended to ground lvl.
2 side ladders replaced with stacked crates.
Added alpha blending to ground texture.
Added rope to side of tower as second means to reach top.
Brightened map, removed rain, and changed skybox texture.
Added slanted window holes to corners of the giant X, by the spawn points.
Changed top of tower to rectangular shape instead of circular one as before.
Optimized map for better loading.

Some suggestions given by LoneIceDragon and Carbon16. Thanks guys.

NOTE: .nav file not included. Run map with bots in it and it will auto-create.
